headline: Boston Beer (SAM) Tops Q3 Earnings Estimates
summary: Boston Beer (SAM) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +12.43% and -0.81%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
